longBusinessSummary: Galway Gold Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral resource properties. It holds interests in the Reina de Oro property located in the Santander mining district of Colombia. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
